==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Go-between
<hw>Go"-be*tween`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A negotiator who
acts as a link between parties; an intermediate agent; a broker; a
procurer; -- sometimes in a disparaging sense.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mediator, intermediator, intermediary.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gobiidae</ent>⟦br⟧
